Module com.example.breakout_clone
Package com.example.breakout_clone.util

Interface Impactable

All Known Implementing Classes:
BallModel, BrickModel, PaddleModel, PowerUpModel
public interface Impactable
This interface provides the functionality for sprites to be impactable. i.e. they can collide with other Imapctable sprites
Author:
Praket Chavan
